query:
SELECT c.id, c.code, c.name, c.projectId, p.code as project_code, p.name as project_name 
FROM constructions c 
LEFT JOIN projects p ON c.projectId = p.id 
ORDER BY c.createdAt DESC 
LIMIT 20;
